The '''65th Annual Tony Awards''' will take place on Sunday, June 12, 2011 and will celebrate the best of [[Broadway theater|Broadway]]. They will be held at the [[Beacon Theatre (New York City)|Beacon Theatre]], ending a fourteen-year tradition of having the ceremony at [[Radio City Music Hall]].<ref name="tonys_announce" /> The Awards will be broadcast [[live television|live]] on [[CBS]] at 8:00pm ([[Eastern Time Zone|eastern]]).<ref name="tonys_announce" /><ref name="bwaycom_tonyannounce" />

==Eligibility==
Shows opening during the 2010 - 2011 Broadway season before April 28, 2011 are eligible.<ref name="tonys_announce" />

